<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="clever-adj">clever <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'klevə(r)/    美 /'klevər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-ame-smart">1.★ <strong>聪明的；机灵的 (AmE smart)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It was clever of him to find his way here.
他能找到这儿来真是聪明。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>巧妙的；机敏的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What a clever idea! 
多么聪明的想法！</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-clever-at">be clever at</h3>
<p>1.<strong>擅长：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The Germans were very clever at inventing things.
德国人非常善于发明东西。</p><footer>译林⑥ – 3</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>cleverly /'klevəli/ adv <br />
cleverness /'klevənəs/ n   </p></div>